{{Quote|''The first Call of Duty style game in VR. 30 Ranks of Levels that save even when you leave world. Guns‚ Perks‚ Killstreaks  What are you waiting for?''}}

'''Gun Em Down''' is a cross-platform FPS game than can be played with up to 16 players. Players are split into teams of 8 max, called americans and germans.

== Gameplay ==
1-16 Players, split into teams, compete to reach 1000 points. The game starts with teams spawning on opposite sides of the map. Some dialogue will play based on the side you are in. Once the dialogue ends, player gains control and can move forward. The match ends when either the 10 minute timer runs out, or the opposing team reaches a max score of 1000 points. These settings are based on the default settings and can be changed by the instance master.

