== Mechanics ==
The player recieves 10 points for every kill.

Players don't lose points by dying. The more kills gotten, the more points get added to the counter.

If a player reaches a certain number of kills without dying, they be rewarded with an item. The item recieved is based on what the player chooses to get in the killstreak locker.

The game contains a perk system that gives the player an advantage. Either by a speed increase (Extreme Conditioning) or a Bullet damage increase (Stopping Power)

Guns are based on which side you are on, but they all work similary. Auto, Semi- Auto, and Manual guns are present.

Players receive only one gun of their choosing. Selectable in the lobby.

