== Tips ==

* Choose perks that help with your weaknesses to get an edge
* Bring a friend. Like any competitive game, its better with a teammate
* Be flexible. Be ready to change perks and playstyle in order to combat opponent strategy
* Always select scout planes as a kill streak. Knowing enemy locations makes getting kills easier
* Pair a technique like B-hopping with extreme conditioning to move faster
* Make the reticle as close to the barrel as possible to improve accuracy
* Use the target practice in the lobby to improve aim

